<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/tech_riders_logo.jpg" type="image/x-icon">
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>AyuLinker - About</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.13.0/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/@google/model-viewer/dist/model-viewer.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="main-content">
        <!-- Navigation -->
        <%- include('navbar') %>


            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <section class="hero-section">
                <div class="hero-container">
                    <div class="hero-text">
                        <h1>Bridging Traditional Medicine and Modern Healthcare</h1>
                        <p>
                            AyuLinker is a FHIR-compliant terminology service that harmonizes
                            India's NAMASTE codes with WHO ICD-11 standards, enabling seamless
                            integration of Ayurveda, Siddha, and Unani medicine into digital
                            health systems.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-visual">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px">
                            <div class="card shadow p-3 card-hover model-container" style="border-radius: 16px">
                                <h6 class="text-center mb-3" style="text-align: start">
                                    🌿 Medicinal Plant Leaf
                                </h6>
                                <model-viewer id="glb" src="/models/leaves/About.glb" alt="Medicinal leaf" auto-rotate
                                    camera-controls shadow-intensity="1" exposure="1" style="
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 400px;
                    min-height: 350px;
                    background: #e5e5e5;
                    border-radius: 12px;">
                                    <div slot="poster" style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;height: 100%;
                      color: #666;background: #f8f9fa;border-radius: 12px;">
                                        <div style="text-align: center">
                                            <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px">🌿</div>
                                            <div>Loading 3D Model...</div>
                                            <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; margin-top: 5px">
                                                Interactive visualization
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </model-viewer>
                                <div class="mb-3 text-center">
                                    <small class="text-muted">Interactive 3D model of medicinal plant leaf</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="leaf-label">
                                    AYUSH: Harmonizing NAMASTE with ICD-11
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Problem and Solution Section -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="content-container problem-solution-grid">
                    <div class="info-card problem-card">
                        <h2>The Interoperability Challenge</h2>
                        <p>
                            India's Ayush sector is transitioning to digital health systems
                            but faces significant challenges in standardizing terminology
                            across traditional and modern medicine practices.
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Different coding standards (NAMASTE vs ICD-11)</li>
                            <li>Interoperability gaps between systems</li>
                            <li>Challenges in insurance & patient records</li>
                            <li>National & international reporting issues</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="info-card solution-card">
                        <h2>Our Solution</h2>
                        <p>AyuLinker provides a standardized terminology service that:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Maps NAMASTE codes to ICD-11 TM2 and Biomedicine codes</li>
                            <li>Provides FHIR-compliant APIs for EMR integration</li>
                            <li>Ensures compliance with India's 2016 EHR Standards</li>
                            <li>Enables dual-coding for traditional & modern medicine</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Features Section -->
            <section class="features-section">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <h2 class="section-title">AyuLinker Key Features</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">
                        Seamless integration of traditional medicine into digital health
                        ecosystems
                    </p>
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">🌿</div>
                            <h3>Terminology Mapping</h3>
                            <p>
                                Bi-directional mapping between NAMASTE, WHO Ayurveda
                                Terminologies, and ICD-11 with AI suggestions.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                            <h3>FHIR-Compliant API</h3>
                            <p>
                                RESTful API for terminology lookup, expansion, and code
                                translation compliant with FHIR R4.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
                            <h3>Secure & Compliant</h3>
                            <p>
                                OAuth 2.0 with ABHA, ISO 22600 access control, and audit trails.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
                            <h3>Real-time Sync</h3>
                            <p>
                                Auto-updates with WHO ICD-API for always-current terminology.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
                            <h3>Advanced Search</h3>
                            <p>
                                Smart search with auto-complete returning both NAMASTE and
                                ICD-11 codes.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                            <h3>Analytics & Reporting</h3>
                            <p>
                                Real-time morbidity analytics aligned with Ayush & WHO
                                reporting.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- How It Works -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <h2 class="section-title">How AyuLinker Works</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">
                        Our service integrates seamlessly with EMR systems for dual-coding
                    </p>
                    <div class="problem-solution-grid">
                        <div class="info-card">
                            <h3>1. Ingest</h3>
                            <p>NAMASTE CSV → FHIR CodeSystem resources</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="info-card">
                            <h3>2. Map</h3>
                            <p>
                                Create ConceptMaps between NAMASTE, Ayurveda, and ICD-11 codes
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="info-card">
                            <h3>3. Sync</h3>
                            <p>Keep codes updated via WHO ICD-API</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="info-card">
                            <h3>4. Serve</h3>
                            <p>FHIR APIs deliver terminology services to EMRs</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Technical Specifications -->
            <section class="features-section">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Technical Specifications</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">
                        Compliant with India's EHR Standards & global specifications
                    </p>
                    <div class="features-grid">
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">📜</div>
                            <h3>Standards Compliance</h3>
                            <p>FHIR R4, SNOMED CT, LOINC, ISO 22600, OAuth 2.0.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">🖥️</div>
                            <h3>API Endpoints</h3>
                            <p>
                                CodeSystem, ValueSet, ConceptMap with $translate operations.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">⚙️</div>
                            <h3>Integration Features</h3>
                            <p>
                                Lightweight micro-service, EMR widgets, dual-coding storage.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">🔐</div>
                            <h3>Security & Audit</h3>
                            <p>
                                Consent mgmt, ABHA integration, audit trails, version tracking.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- New Feature 1 -->
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">☁️</div>
                            <h3>Cloud Ready</h3>
                            <p>Scalable deployment on our own server and easily accessible from anywhere in the world.</p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- New Feature 2 -->
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                            <h3>Analytics & Reporting</h3>
                            <p>
                                Real-time dashboards, terminology usage metrics, and predictive insights.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>


            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <section class="cta-section">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <div class="cta-card">
                        <h2 class="section-title">🌿 Ready to Integrate AyuLinker?</h2>
                        <p class="section-subtitle">
                            Empower your healthcare systems with interoperability. Try our
                            demo, explore the GitHub repo, or get in touch with us directly.
                        </p>
                        <div class="cta-buttons">
                            <a href="/" class="cta-button">🚀 View Live Demo</a>
                            <a href="https://github.com/sagniksaha279/AyuLinker.git" target="_blank"
                                class="cta-button secondary">💻
                                GitHub Repository</a>
                            <a href="mailto:contacttechriders@gmail.com" class="cta-button highlight">📩 Contact Us</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <div class="container">
                <img src="/images/tech_riders_logo.jpg" alt="TechRiders Logo" style="border-radius: 50%;">
                <p><b>We're delighted to have you on our website! 😊</b></p>
                <p>Thanks for making it awesome just by being here! 🎉</p>

